profile:
We're Always Here For You
E.T. Mechanical Ltd. specializes in HVAC (Heating, Ventillation, Air Conditioning), Electrical, and  Plumbing Services within Fredericton, NB and surrounding areas.

What we offer:
The Best People (Installation, Information Sharing, Client Relations)
The Best Service (Quality of Maintenance, Availability, Customer Education)
The Best Comfort (System is tailored to home, Comfort Needs Accessed. Year Round Comfort)
The Best Return on Investment
When you choose E.T. Mechanical you choose peace of mind. We have highly trained and licensed technicians in every field, HVAC, plumbers, electricians, oil , gas, and geothermal. We offer a full range of home services including  radon testing and mitigation and asbestos abatement.

We do what is best for our clients, their families and their homes to give the biggest return on their investment and assure their family's comfort and safety.

Please visit our website to see what we're doing to protect both our customers and employees during this time of COVID-19.
